<li>Travel against medical advice or for the purpose of obtaining medical treatment</li>
<li>Expenses incurred as a consequence of the use of alcohol or drugs or arising out of any sexually transmitted disease</li>
<li>Any Medical Expenses in excess of £300 and any repatriation expenses incurred without the prior approval of IMG</li>
<li>Dental/optical treatment other than for immediate relief of pain</li>
<li>Routine management or monitoring of pre- existing medical conditions</li>
<li>Air travel other than as a passenger</li>
